'''Xextese''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Xexto/Legends|Xexto]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Troiken/Legends|Troiken]]. Most Xexto were fluent in both Xextese and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.

"Challat" meant "flesh" in Xextese.

